title: Offseason Fun, Dynasty Decisions, Happy Twosday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 2/22
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason answer a number of listener questions of all kinds! Redraft, keeper, dynasty, food, and more! Plus, NFL News including the latest on Aaron Rodgers. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for February 22nd, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(06:00) - NFL News
(13:30) - Quick Question: Michael Thomas Top 10 Potential?
(19:10) - Mailbag
(20:50) - Keeper vs Dynasty
(24:20) - Broncos, too many mouths to feed?
(27:40) - Total Points League
(30:40) - James Robinson Dynasty value
(31:15) - No-No Words
(33:15) - Transitioning to a bigger league
(35:10) - Consistency Rank Algorithm 
(36:50) - Breakfast Food Rank: Pancakes, Waffles, French Toast
(39:10) - Dynasty Trade: D.J. Moore for Rookie 1.02
